      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DUNSTALL THE GUN (7) gets in light with the 2kg claim and is ready to win with his get-back racing pattern. Warmed up late with the 59kg when third over 1600m at Scone. Drawn a low gate today and should get enough speed to finish over the top of these. SMART BUY (6) gives the impression she's ready for the 1600m after running on late at all four runs this time in. Gave away a big start on the turn before chipping away late to secure fifth over 1450m at Muswellbrook. Look for her late. SET TO PROPHET (3) turned his form around this campaign and chasing his third-straight win today. Taken to the front and never headed as fav with a comfortable victory over 1400m at this track. Proven over the 1600m and the claim helps again. SANBINA (10) improving mare who got off the mark at start four in her first campaign over the 1400m here. Bred to get this trip and further and deserves her chance in this tougher contest. Keep safe.",
